89
00:05:43,583 --> 00:05:44,541
[ELFMAN] What's
she doing to you?!

90
00:05:44,625 --> 00:05:46,458
[LISANNA] Mira!

91
00:05:46,541 --> 00:05:48,541
[MARY] Conducting Art:
Second Movement!

92
00:05:48,625 --> 00:05:50,291
