use this technique

93
00:05:50,375 --> 00:05:52,875
but I'll totes make
an exception for you!

94
00:05:52,958 --> 00:05:55,875
[pained scream]

95
00:05:55,958 --> 00:05:58,083
[LISANNA] Something's
coming out of her body!

96
00:05:58,166 --> 00:05:59,833
[ELFMAN] It's
her Satan Soul!

97
00:06:01,458 --> 00:06:02,291
