take this "sibling rivalry"!

101
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,875
[demonic breathing]

102
00:06:09,958 --> 00:06:11,083
[LISANNA]
No, not us!

103
00:06:11,166 --> 00:06:12,458
[ELFMAN growls]

104
00:06:12,541 --> 00:06:14,250
