105
00:06:17,875 --> 00:06:19,750
[MARY] This is so
freakin' awesome!

106
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:30,250
Oh no?! How're we
gonna get out of this?!

107
00:06:30,333 --> 00:06:32,583
[MARY] This is, like,
the greatest thing ever!

108
00:06:32,666 --> 00:06:36,083
Anyone who dares to defy
the archbishop is totes bad!

109
00:06:36,166 --> 00:06:40,291
And all bad people have,
like, gotta be punished!

110
00:06:42,916 --> 00:06:44,083
[DROY] That fight
between you and Sammy

111
00:06:44,166 --> 00:06:45,583
was somethin' else, Lily!

112
00:06:45,666 --> 00:06:48,125
[JET] Yeah, I've never seen
two Exceeds go at it before.

113
00:06:48,208 --> 00:06:49,500
It was nuts.

114
00:06:49,583 --> 00:06:50,916
There's so few
of you guys around,

115
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:53,333
it's a shame you
can't all be friends.

116
00:06:53,416 --> 00:06:55,541
[PANTHERLILY] He's a rather
impertinent fellow, I'm afraid.

117
00:06:55,625 --> 00:06:56,833
While we're
on the subject...

118
00:06:56,916 --> 00:06:58,416
Yeah, what's
the big deal?

119
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,291
Why has Sammy
been following us?

120
00:07:01,541 --> 00:07:03,833
Because he's a
stubborn fool.

121
00:07:03,916 --> 00:07:06,333
I am not a fool and
I am not following you...

122
00:07:06,416 --> 00:07:08,166
I am merely observing you.

123
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:09,916
Just so we're clear,
you're not getting'

124
